<html>
<head> 
	<title>Ruffle - Anonymous Picture Messaging to Any Phone Number</title>
	<meta name="description" content="Send an Anonymous Picture Message to any Phone Number via SMS. Start Ruffling your friends.">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicon.ico">

	<!-- Facebook Open Graph meta -->
	<meta property="og:type" content="website">
	<meta property="og:url" content="http://ruffle.us/p/{{=it.photoId}}">
	<meta property="og:title" content="Someone Ruffled Me With This Anonymous Picture Message!">
	<meta property="og:description" content="Send an Anonymous Picture Message to any Phone Number via SMS. Start Ruffling your friends.">
	<meta property="og:image" content="http://s3.amazonaws.com/ruffle/{{=it.photoId}}">
	<meta property="og:site_name" content="Ruffle">

	<!-- Twitter Cards meta -->
	<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
	<meta name="twitter:site" content="@ruffleapp">
	<meta name="twitter:url" content="http://ruffle.us/p/{{=it.photoId}}">
	<meta name="twitter:title" content="Someone Ruffled Me With This Anonymous Picture Message!">
	<meta name="twitter:description" content="Send an Anonymous Picture Message to any Phone Number via SMS. Start Ruffling your friends.">
	<meta name="twitter:image:src" content="http://s3.amazonaws.com/ruffle/{{=it.photoId}}">

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/ruffle.css">
</head>
<body>
	<div class="background">
		<div class="column">

			<div class="title">
				<img class="title-img" src="/images/title.png"/>
			</div>

			<p class="about">
				You have received this anonymous Ruffle (picture message) from one of your friends. 
			</p>

			<img class="ruffle" src="http://s3.amazonaws.com/ruffle/{{=it.photoId}}"/>

			<div class="gapme">
				<a class="btn" href="http://ruffle.us"><span class="fa fa-camera"></span> Send someone a Ruffle</a>
			</div>
			<div class="gapme">
				<a class="btn" href="http://ruffle.us/reruffle/{{=it.photoId}}"><span class="fa fa-camera"></span> Re-Ruffle this photo</a>
			</div>

			<div class="sharing">
				<a class="fb" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://ruffle.us/p/{{=it.photoId}}" target="_blank"><span class="fa fa-facebook-square"></span> Share</a>
				<a class="twit" href="https://twitter.com/home?status=Someone%20Ruffled%20me!%20Check%20it%20out!%20http://ruffle.us/p/{{=it.photoId}}%20%23ruffle" target="_blank"><span class="fa fa-twitter"></span>Twitter</a>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-title">
				What is this?
			</div>
			<div class="faq">
				Ruffle lets you send an anonymous picture message to anyone with a phone number via SMS. You’ll know who you’re sending it to, but they won’t know who’s Ruffling them.
			</div>
			<div class="faq-title">
				How Anonymous Is Ruffle?
			</div>
			<div class="faq">
				We don’t record or attach any information about a message sender. When you send someone a Ruffle, they will receive an SMS from “Ruffle.us” or an anonymous phone number. Unless you send a photo of your face, they will have no idea who sent it.
			</div>
			<div class="faq-title">
				Want to chat?
			</div>
			<div class="faq twits">
				<a class="contact-link" href="http://www.twitter.com/nickdrewe" target="_blank">@nickdrewe</a> <a class="contact-link" href="http://www.twitter.com/_mattway" target="_blank">@_mattway</a>
			</div>
			<div class="faq">
				Send us an email at <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:rufflesms@gmail.com">rufflesms@gmail.com</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<script>
